'''''Peterson's Guide to Droids of the Republic''''' was a comprehensive catalogue of the different types of [[Droid/Legends|droids]] in known space, available in searchable format over the [[HoloNet/Legends|HoloNet]] in the last days of the [[Galactic Republic/Legends|Galactic Republic]]. The entry on the [[Tac-Spec Corporation|Tac-Spec]] [[FIII Footman droid|Footman droid]] was in the catalog's seventh volume, entitled ''The Great Corporate Expansion Era''.

